What has everything to do with the problem is Boeing's corporate culture.  Somewhere along the line, Boeing's culture approached making these flying beasts as if they were a Pizza chain. Where job number one is short term profit, and safety and the product itself is more of a pain in the ass than a mission. </p><p>

